---

<!-- Features Section -->
<section class="py-24 bg-white" id="features">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <!-- Section heading with decorative elements -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 relative inline-block">
        Why is it so great?
        <div class="absolute -bottom-2 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-400 to-primary-600 rounded-full"></div>
      </h2>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Features grid with playful design -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      
      <!-- Active Community Feature -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 p-6 group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary-500/10 mb-6 mx-auto lg:mx-0 group-hover:bg-primary-500/20 transition-colors">
          <i class="fa fa-comments text-2xl text-primary-500"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 text-center lg:text-left">Active Community</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-center lg:text-left">
          Why not take a look at our amazing community? Our users are just amazing, and thanks to them our community is a really nice place to share your doubts, projects or suggestions related with Kodular.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Our Team Feature -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 p-6 group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary-500/10 mb-6 mx-auto lg:mx-0 group-hover:bg-primary-500/20 transition-colors">
          <i class="fa fa-users text-2xl text-primary-500"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 text-center lg:text-left">Our Team</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-center lg:text-left">
          Our Team is very enthusiastic and loves helping people. They will really like to help you on the road to create an app. We are devotees of the IT!
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Maximum Stability Feature -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 p-6 group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary-500/10 mb-6 mx-auto lg:mx-0 group-hover:bg-primary-500/20 transition-colors">
          <i class="fa fa-server text-2xl text-primary-500"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 text-center lg:text-left">Maximum Stability</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-center lg:text-left">
          Kodular Infrastructure is powered by our partner ArubaCloud, which guarantees a really good uptime and performance.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Other Services Feature -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 p-6 group">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary-500/10 mb-6 mx-auto lg:mx-0 group-hover:bg-primary-500/20 transition-colors">
          <i class="fa fa-plus text-2xl text-primary-500"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 text-center lg:text-left">Other Services!</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-center lg:text-left">
          We provide more than just an <a href="/creator" class="text-primary-500 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">App Creator</a>. We also have a self-developed <a href="/store" class="text-primary-500 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">App Store</a>, an online <a href="/ide" class="text-primary-500 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Extensions IDE</a> and an <a href="/account" class="text-primary-500 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">Account Control Panel</a>. Let's expand Kodular!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
